%% 3.2.5 View Child Detail — sequence
%% GET /api/Student/Get/{id} — ensure student.GuardianId matches token (enforce in backend policy)
%% BR20: Read-only for guardians — no PUT from app

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant SC as StudentController
    participant SS as StudentService
    participant Repo as IRepository Student
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Tap child card
    App->>SC: GET /api/Student/Get/{id} Bearer
    SC->>SS: GetStudentByIdAsync(id)
    SS->>Repo: Include Guardian, Campus
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    SS-->>SC: StudentDto
    SC-->>App: 200 OK
    App->>Guardian: Demographics, class (if modeled), Face ID / leave actions (UI)
